tion", "ayah_number": 6132, "text": "un Messager, de la part d'Allah, qui leur r\u00e9cite des feuilles purifi\u00e9es,"}, {"id": 336330, "identifier": "fr.hamidullah", "surah_number": 98, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0646\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Bayyina", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Evidence", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 30, "manzil": 7, "page": 598, "ruku": 540, "hizb_quarter": 239, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "fr", "name": "Hamidullah", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Hamidullah", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 6132, "text": "un Messager, de la part d'Allah, qui leur r\u00e9cite des feuilles purifi\u00e9es,"}, {"id": 336003, "identifier": "fr.hamidullah", "surah_number": 98, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0646\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Bayyina", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Evidence", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 30, "manzil": 7, "page": 598, "ruku": 540, "hizb_quarter": 239, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "fr", "name": "Hamidullah", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Hamidullah", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 6133, "text": "dans lesquelles se trouvent des prescriptions d'une rectitude parfaite."}, {"id": 336332, "identifier": "fr.hamidullah", "surah_number": 98, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0646\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Bayyina", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Evidence", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 30, "manzil": 7, "page": 598, "ruku": 540, "hizb_quarter": 239, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "fr", "name": "Hamidullah", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Hamidullah", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 6133, "text": "dans lesquelles se trouvent des prescriptions d'une rectitude parfaite."}, {"id": 336007, "identifier": "fr.hamidullah", "surah_number": 98, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0646\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Bayyina", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Evidence", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 30, "manzil": 7, "page": 598, "ruku": 540, "hizb_quarter": 239, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "fr", "name": "Hamidullah", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Hamidullah", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 6134, "text": "Et ceux \u00e0 qui le Livre a \u00e9t\u00e9 donn\u00e9 ne se sont divis\u00e9s qu'apr\u00e8s que la preuve leur fut venue."}, {"id": 336336, "identifier": "fr.hamidullah", "surah_number": 98, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0646\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Bayyina", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Evidence", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 30, "manzil": 7, "page": 598, "ruku": 540, "hizb_quarter": 239, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "fr", "name": "Hamidullah", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Hamidullah", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 6134, "text": "Et ceux \u00e0 qui le Livre a \u00e9t\u00e9 donn\u00e9 ne se sont divis\u00e9s qu'apr\u00e8s que la preuve leur fut venue."}, {"id": 336010, "identifier": "fr.hamidullah", "surah_number": 98, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0646\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Bayyina", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Evidence", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 30, "manzil": 7, "page": 598, "ruku": 540, "hizb_quarter": 239, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "fr", "name": "Hamidullah", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Hamidullah", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 6135, "text": "Il ne leur a \u00e9t\u00e9 command\u00e9, cependant, que d'adorer Allah, Lui vouant un culte exclusif, d'accomplir la Sal\u00e2t et d'acquitter la Zak\u00e2t. Et voil\u00e0 la religion de droiture."}, {"id": 336338, "identifier": "fr.hamidullah", "surah_number": 98, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0646\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Bayyina", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Evidence", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 30, "manzil": 7, "page": 598, "ruku": 540, "hizb_quarter": 239, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "fr", "name": "Hamidullah", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Hamidullah", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 6135, "text": "Il ne leur a \u00e9t\u00e9 command\u00e9, cependant, que d'adorer Allah, Lui vouant un culte exclusif, d'accomplir la Sal\u00e2t et d'acquitter la Zak\u00e2t. Et voil\u00e0 la religion de droiture."}, {"id": 336012, "identifier": "fr.hamidullah", "surah_number": 98, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0646\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Bayyina", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Evidence", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 30, "manzil": 7, "page": 598, "ruku": 540, "hizb_quarter": 239, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "fr", "name": "Hamidullah", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Hamidullah", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 6136, "text": "Les infid\u00e8les parmi les gens du Livre, ainsi que les Associateurs iront au feu de l'Enfer, pour y demeurer \u00e9ternellement. De toute la cr\u00e9ation, ce sont eux les pires."}, {"id": 336340, "identifier": "fr.hamidullah", "surah_number": 98, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0646\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Bayyina", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Evidence", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 30, "manzil": 7, "page": 598, "ruku": 540, "hizb_quarter": 239, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "fr", "name": "Hamidullah", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Hamidullah", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 6136, "text": "Les infid\u00e8les parmi les gens du Livre, ainsi que les Associateurs iront au feu de l'Enfer, pour y demeurer \u00e9ternellement. De toute la cr\u00e9ation, ce sont eux les pires."}, {"id": 336014, "identifier": "fr.hamidullah", "surah_number": 98, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0646\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Bayyina", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Evidence", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 30, "manzil": 7, "page": 598, "ruku": 540, "hizb_quarter": 239, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "fr", "name": "Hamidullah", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Hamidullah", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 6137, "text": "Quant \u00e0 ceux qui croient et accomplissent les bonnes \u0153uvres, ce sont les meilleurs de toute la cr\u00e9ation."}, {"id": 336342, "identifier": "fr.hamidullah", "surah_number": 98, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0646\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Bayyina", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Evidence", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 30, "manzil": 7, "page": 598, "ruku": 540, "hizb_quarter": 239, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "fr", "name": "Hamidullah", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Hamidullah", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 6137, "text": "Quant \u00e0 ceux qui croient et accomplissent les bonnes \u0153uvres, ce sont les meilleurs de toute la cr\u00e9ation."}, {"id": 336016, "identifier": "fr.hamidullah", "surah_number": 98, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0646\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Bayyina", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Evidence", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 30, "manzil": 7, "page": 599, "ruku": 540, "hizb_quarter": 239, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "fr", "name": "Hamidullah", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Hamidullah", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 6138, "text": "Leur r\u00e9compense aupr\u00e8s d'Allah sera les Jardins de s\u00e9jour, sous lesquels coulent les ruisseaux, pour y demeurer \u00e9ternellement. Allah les agr\u00e9e et ils L'agr\u00e9ent. Telle sera [la r\u00e9compense] de celui qui craint son Seigneur."}, {"id": 336344, "identifier": "fr.hamidullah", "surah_number": 98, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0646\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Bayyina", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Evidence", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 30, "manzil": 7, "page": 599, "ruku": 540, "hizb_quarter": 239, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "fr", "name": "Hamidullah", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Hamidullah", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 6138, "text": "Leur r\u00e9compense aupr\u00e8s d'Allah sera les Jardins de s\u00e9jour, sous lesquels coulent les ruisseaux, pour y demeurer \u00e9ternellement. Allah les agr\u00e9e et ils L'agr\u00e9ent. Telle sera [la r\u00e9compense] de celui qui craint son Seigneur."}]